name: Jumpstart v2
tagline: Version 2 of a quick start template for sites, apps and prototypes - based on the Yeoman Gulp Webapp Generator with added Jade templating.
body: This scaffolding is based on Yeoman - install all the usual dependencies to get that running on your system, then do `npm install` and `bower install` to get the site's local dependencies and tooling installed. Once that is done you can `gulp serve` to spin up the development server with live-reload and `gulp` to build for distribution.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
